name: Michelson OG 1/1
description:
Tribute to Michelson, the programming language used to code smart contracts on Tezos.

A Michelson OG is quite a rare breed. 

This artwork is a 1/1 and is the only animated from the collection "Michelson".

Each frame composing this animated loop is unique. When I create a new artwork, I work on a frame by frame basis.

Token's owner can use each frame as a PFP. This artwork is composed of 25 frames in total.
